   20: -module(user_skip_4_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -compile(export_all).
   23: 
   24: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   25: 
   26: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   27: %% Function: suite() -> Info
   28: %% Info = [tuple()]
   29: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   30: suite() ->
   31:     [{timetrap,{seconds,30}}].
   32: 
   33: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   34: %% Function: init_per_suite(Config0) ->
   35: %%               Config1 | {skip,Reason} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
   36: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   37: %% Reason = term()
   38: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   39: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   40:     Config.
   41: 
   42: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   43: %% Function: end_per_suite(Config0) -> void() | {save_config,Config1}
   44: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   45: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   46: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   47:     ok.
   48: 
   49: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   50: %% Function: init_per_group(GroupName, Config0) ->
   51: %%               Config1 | {skip,Reason} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
   52: %% GroupName = atom()
   53: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   54: %% Reason = term()
   55: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   56: init_per_group(g1, _Config) ->
   57:     {skip,"Group skipped"};
   58: init_per_group(g3, _Config) ->
   59:     {skip,"Group skipped"};
   60: init_per_group(g6, _Config) ->
   61:     {skip,"Group skipped"};
   62: init_per_group(_, Config) ->
   63:     Config.
   64: 
   65: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   66: %% Function: end_per_group(GroupName, Config0) ->
   67: %%               void() | {save_config,Config1}
   68: %% GroupName = atom()
   69: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   70: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   71: end_per_group(_GroupName, _Config) ->
   72:     ok.
   73: 
   74: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   75: %% Function: init_per_testcase(TestCase, Config0) ->
   76: %%               Config1 | {skip,Reason} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
   77: %% TestCase = atom()
   78: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   79: %% Reason = term()
   80: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   81: init_per_testcase(_, Config) ->
   82:     Config.
   83: 
   84: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   85: %% Function: end_per_testcase(TestCase, Config0) ->
   86: %%               void() | {save_config,Config1}
   87: %% TestCase = atom()
   88: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
   89: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   90: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, _Config) ->
   91:     ok.
   92: 
   93: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
   94: %% Function: groups() -> [Group]
   95: %% Group = {GroupName,Properties,GroupsAndTestCases}
   96: %% GroupName = atom()
   97: %% Properties = [parallel | sequence | Shuffle | {RepeatType,N}]
   98: %% GroupsAndTestCases = [Group | {group,GroupName} | TestCase]
   99: %% TestCase = atom()
  100: %% Shuffle = shuffle | {shuffle,{integer(),integer(),integer()}}
  101: %% RepeatType = repeat | repeat_until_all_ok | repeat_until_all_fail |
  102: %%              repeat_until_any_ok | repeat_until_any_fail
  103: %% N = integer() | forever
  104: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  105: groups() ->
  106:     [{g1,[],[tc1,tc2]},
  107:      {g2,[],[tc3,tc4]},
  108:      {g3,[],[tc5,{g4,[],[tc6,tc7]},tc8]},
  109:      {g5,[],[tc9,{g6,[],[tc10,tc11]}]}].
  110: 
  111: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  112: %% Function: all() -> GroupsAndTestCases | {skip,Reason}
  113: %% GroupsAndTestCases = [{group,GroupName} | TestCase]
  114: %% GroupName = atom()
  115: %% TestCase = atom()
  116: %% Reason = term()
  117: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  118: all() -> 
  119:     [{group,g1}, {group,g2}, {group,g3}, {group,g5}].
  120: 
  121: 
  122: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  123: %% Function: TestCase(Config0) ->
  124: %%               ok | exit() | {skip,Reason} | {comment,Comment} |
  125: %%               {save_config,Config1} | {skip_and_save,Reason,Config1}
  126: %% Config0 = Config1 = [tuple()]
  127: %% Reason = term()
  128: %% Comment = term()
  129: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  130: tc1(_) ->
  131:     ok.
  132: tc2(_) ->
  133:     ok.
  134: tc3(_) ->
  135:     ok.
  136: tc4(_) ->
  137:     ok.
  138: tc5(_) ->
  139:     ok.
  140: tc6(_) ->
  141:     ok.
  142: tc7(_) ->
  143:     ok.
  144: tc8(_) ->
  145:     ok.
  146: tc9(_) ->
  147:     ok.
  148: tc10(_) ->
  149:     ok.
  150: tc11(_) ->
  151:     ok.
